KATSINA – Alhaji Mustapha Muhammed Inuwa, the Secretary to the Government of Katsina State has Thursday resigned from office. This is coming barely weeks of speculation following the instructions given for all contestants for elective positions to retire immediately. Abdullahi Yaradua, the Chief Press Secretary to the SGS, when contacted affirmed the information, saying, the press would soon be properly briefed. Details later……